===========================================create virtual env======================

check python version:
python3 --version

Check pip version:
python3 -m pip --version

create virtual environment:
python3 -m venv env ('env' name your own choice)
To activate:
source env/bin/activate
To deactivate:
deactivate env
To install or upgrade pip:
cd pip_instal> pip3 install --upgrade pip

=============================

To install django:
pip install django (if not mention version like django=3.1, it will install latest version of django)


To check 
pip freeze

Error:
TypeError: argument of type 'PosixPath' is not iterable
==============================
To uninstallation python:
To check version: python3 --version
To check pip version: pip --version
To check location of installed python: which python3
Go to installed location of python:cmd+shift+G
copy this location upto framework then pest it go to finder
Remove python folder in that location
Remove python application from mac application
check python installation again from terminal: python3 --version
check the pip installation again in terminal: pip3 --version


terminal: cd /usr/bin
> ls -la py*
>python3 --version
